            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><span class=\"paragraph\">Just to get you comfortable with editing and running code, click into the cell above, and edit the code.  I recommend trying to multiply numbers.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Below I've just got a BUNCH of cells of code for you to run.  They code is all short and demonstrates relatively simple behavior.  Rather than bore you with long text, I'll leave the cells as puzzles.  Why do they behave the way they do?</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Feel free to tinker and toy with them, to see modifications of their behavior.</span></span>"
